-- Hochtief Unit Secures Financial Close on Police Stations PPP in Ontario
-- Mike Gavin
-- 2010-09-20T08:36:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/hochtief-unit-secures-financial-close-on-police-stations-ppp-in-ontario.html

          
          
             Hochtief AG said a unit has reached
financial close on a public-private partnership in Canada.
Hochtief PPP Solutions has been contracted to design, build,
finance and maintain 18 provincial police facilities in Ontario,
a project with a contract volume of 306 million euros, the
company said in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        